title: 5 Dev machine 110g Titanium Stem in California, plus wild-looking 7075 Cranks & eCranks
content:
5th Axis, a self-described world leader in manufacturing complex components for the aerospace and medical industries, has created a new bicycle componentry division, 5 Dev.
